    <title>Hexo + Next: A Sample Page Showcase</title>
    <url>/2024/11/09/samples-references/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>This page is hidden until you click the ‘ Read More ‘ button.<br>在您按下「閱讀全文」內容按鈕前，此頁面已被隱藏。</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<!-- Cutdown -->
<h1 id="Introduction"><a href="#Introduction" class="headerlink" title="Introduction"></a>Introduction</h1><p>This is a sample page for showcasing diffirent functions of hexo posting.<br>You may link yourself to diffirent functions by the left sidebar.<br>Reference:<br><a href="https://zenreal.github.io/posts/44730/#">https://zenreal.github.io/posts/44730/#</a></p>
<h1 id="Common-Functions"><a href="#Common-Functions" class="headerlink" title="Common Functions"></a>Common Functions</h1><!-- Cutdown -->
<h2 id="Header"><a href="#Header" class="headerlink" title="Header"></a>Header</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># This will be Header of Introduction.</span><br><span class="line">## This will be the second Header, which is the current &#x27;Header&#x27;.</span><br><span class="line">### This will be the third Header.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>Header can link user to a specific location.</p>
<!-- Cutdown -->
<h2 id="How-to-display-a-Image"><a href="#How-to-display-a-Image" class="headerlink" title="How to display a Image"></a>How to display a Image</h2><p>To display a image, there are four ways.</p>
<!-- Cutdown -->
<h3 id="1-Using-center-to-locate-the-image-at-center"><a href="#1-Using-center-to-locate-the-image-at-center" class="headerlink" title="1: Using center to locate the image at center."></a>1: Using center to locate the image at center.</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;center&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;img src=&quot;/images/sample_image.jpg&quot; width=&quot;50%&quot; height=&quot;50%&quot; /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">Center image</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/center&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<center>
<img src="/images/sample_image.jpg" width="50%" height="50%" />
Center image with size control
</center>

<h3 id="2-Using-single-line-to-display-image"><a href="#2-Using-single-line-to-display-image" class="headerlink" title="2: Using single line to display image."></a>2: Using single line to display image.</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![Image Descrption](https://i.ibb.co/JkCKQFQ/sample-image.jpg)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="https://i.ibb.co/JkCKQFQ/sample-image.jpg" alt="Image_by_link"></p>
<center>
Center image by single line . Put link/source to the right.
</center>

<h3 id="3-Using-Group-Pictures-to-put-mutiple-images"><a href="#3-Using-Group-Pictures-to-put-mutiple-images" class="headerlink" title="3: Using Group Pictures to put mutiple images."></a>3: Using Group Pictures to put mutiple images.</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% gp [1]-[1] %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">![image description](https://i.ibb.co/JkCKQFQ/sample-image.jpg)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endgp %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<div class="group-picture"><div class="group-picture-row"><div class="group-picture-column"><img src="https://i.ibb.co/JkCKQFQ/sample-image.jpg" alt="image description"></div></div></div>
<center>
A fully filled center image by GP , with 1 image and layout 1.
</center>
<br>

<hr>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% grouppicture 4-4 %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">![Sample_img](sample.jpg)</span><br><span class="line">![Sample_img](sample.jpg)</span><br><span class="line">![Sample_img](sample.jpg)</span><br><span class="line">![Sample_img](sample.jpg)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endgrouppicture %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<div class="group-picture"><div class="group-picture-row"><div class="group-picture-column"><img src="/sample.jpg" alt="Sample_img"></div><div class="group-picture-column"><img src="/sample.jpg" alt="Sample_img"></div><div class="group-picture-column"><img src="/sample.jpg" alt="Sample_img"></div></div><div class="group-picture-row"><div class="group-picture-column"><img src="/sample.jpg" alt="Sample_img"></div></div></div>

<center>
A grouped center image by GP , with 4 images and layout 3.
<br>
For layout usages, check <a href="https://theme-next.js.org/docs/tag-plugins/group-pictures">https://theme-next.js.org/docs/tag-plugins/group-pictures</a>
</center>

<h3 id="4-Using-HTML-‘s-div-block-to-locate-the-image-on-left"><a href="#4-Using-HTML-‘s-div-block-to-locate-the-image-on-left" class="headerlink" title="4: Using HTML ‘s div block to locate the image on left."></a>4: Using HTML ‘s div block to locate the image on left.</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;div style=&quot;display:inline-block;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;img width=&quot;100%&quot; style=&quot;float:left; margin-right: 10px;&quot; </span><br><span class="line">src=&quot;/images/sample_image.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;$fileName&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<div style="display:inline-block;"><img width="100%" style="float:left; margin-right: 10px;" src="/images/sample_image.jpg" alt="$fileName"></div>

<h2 id="Linking-function"><a href="#Linking-function" class="headerlink" title="Linking function"></a>Linking function</h2><p>In default, link would be shown as normal text. ( Eg. <a href="https://ravennanma.github.io/">https://ravennanma.github.io/</a> )<br>But there are two common ways to show links.</p>
<h3 id="1-First-method"><a href="#1-First-method" class="headerlink" title="1: First method"></a>1: First method</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[Shown Text](https://yourlink.com)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><a href="https://ravennanma.github.io/">For example: My Github</a></p>
<h3 id="2-Second-method"><a href="#2-Second-method" class="headerlink" title="2: Second method"></a>2: Second method</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;a href=&quot;https://ravennanma.github.io/&quot;&gt;https://ravennanma.github.io/&lt;/a&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><a href="https://ravennanma.github.io/">https://ravennanma.github.io/</a></p>
<h2 id="Text-Styles"><a href="#Text-Styles" class="headerlink" title="Text Styles"></a>Text Styles</h2><p>This is a nomral text without styles.</p>
<h3 id="Italic"><a href="#Italic" class="headerlink" title="Italic"></a><em>Italic</em></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*This will be Italic*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="Bold"><a href="#Bold" class="headerlink" title="Bold"></a><strong>Bold</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">**This will be Bold**</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="Bold-Italic"><a href="#Bold-Italic" class="headerlink" title="Bold Italic"></a><em><strong>Bold Italic</strong></em></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">***This will be Bold Italic**</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="Deletion-line"><a href="#Deletion-line" class="headerlink" title="Deletion line"></a><del>Deletion line</del></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">~~This will be Deletion line~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="Underline"><a href="#Underline" class="headerlink" title="Underline"></a><u>Underline</u></h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;u&gt;This will be Underline&lt;/u&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Common-Text-functions"><a href="#Common-Text-functions" class="headerlink" title="Common Text functions"></a>Common Text functions</h2><p>These are some common functions when typing text.</p>
<h3 id="Changing-font-colors"><a href="#Changing-font-colors" class="headerlink" title="Changing font colors"></a>Changing font colors</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;font color=#008080&gt;Color Teat has been shown.&lt;/font&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><font color=#008080>Color Teat has been shown.</font><br>You may find common colors at <a href="https://www.rapidtables.com/web/color/html-color-codes.html">here</a>.<br>Or use a online picker at <a href="https://htmlcolorcodes.com/color-picker/">here</a>.</p>
<h2 id="Special-Line"><a href="#Special-Line" class="headerlink" title="Special Line"></a>Special Line</h2><p>There are diffirent reference line &#x2F; alert messages.</p>
<h3 id="Reference-single-line"><a href="#Reference-single-line" class="headerlink" title="Reference single line"></a>Reference single line</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; This is a single Reference Line</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>This is a single Reference Line</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="Refrence-multiple-line"><a href="#Refrence-multiple-line" class="headerlink" title="Refrence multiple line"></a>Refrence multiple line</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; This is the first Reference Line</span><br><span class="line">&gt; This is the second Reference Line</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>This is the first Reference Line<br>This is the second Reference Line</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="Reference-multiple-stacking-line"><a href="#Reference-multiple-stacking-line" class="headerlink" title="Reference multiple stacking line"></a>Reference multiple stacking line</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; This is the first Reference Line</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; This is the second Reference Line</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>This is the first Reference Line</p>
<blockquote>
<p>This is the second Reference Line</p>
</blockquote>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="Center-reference"><a href="#Center-reference" class="headerlink" title="Center reference"></a>Center reference</h3><!-- 文本居中引用效果 -->
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% cq %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">Center reference effect !</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endcq %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote class="blockquote-center">
<p>Center reference effect !</p>

</blockquote>

<h3 id="Spliting-lines"><a href="#Spliting-lines" class="headerlink" title="Spliting lines"></a>Spliting lines</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">----</span><br><span class="line">This is spliting lines 1.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">***</span><br><span class="line">This is spliting lines 2.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<p>This is spliting lines 1.</p>
<hr>
<p>This is spliting lines 2.</p>
<h2 id="List"><a href="#List" class="headerlink" title="List"></a>List</h2><h3 id="Dot-List"><a href="#Dot-List" class="headerlink" title="Dot List"></a>Dot List</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">+ Dot List 1</span><br><span class="line">+ Dot List 2</span><br><span class="line">    + Dot List 2.1</span><br><span class="line">        + Dot List 2.1.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>Dot List 1</li>
<li>Dot List 2<ul>
<li>Dot List 2.1<ul>
<li>Dot List 2.1.1</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="Number-List"><a href="#Number-List" class="headerlink" title="Number List"></a>Number List</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">+ Dot List 1</span><br><span class="line">+ Dot List 2</span><br><span class="line">    + Dot List 2.1</span><br><span class="line">        + Dot List 2.1.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ol>
<li>Num List 1</li>
<li>Num List 2<ol>
<li>Num List 2.1<ol>
<li>Num List 2.1.1</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="Checked-List"><a href="#Checked-List" class="headerlink" title="Checked List"></a>Checked List</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">- [ ] Target 1</span><br><span class="line">- [x] Target 2</span><br><span class="line">- [x] Target 3</span><br><span class="line">- [ ] Target 4</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Target 1</li>
<li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> Target 2</li>
<li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> Target 3</li>
<li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Target 4</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="Form"><a href="#Form" class="headerlink" title="Form"></a>Form</h2><p>Form can be easily formed no matter the space is placed correctly or not.</p>
<h3 id="Default-Form"><a href="#Default-Form" class="headerlink" title="Default Form"></a>Default Form</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">| Column 1 | Column 2 | Column 3 |</span><br><span class="line">| -------- | -------- | -------- |</span><br><span class="line">| Text1    | Text2    | Text3    |</span><br><span class="line">| Text4    | Text5    | Text6    |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<table>
