<h2 id="Common-Text-Funtions"><a href="#Common-Text-Funtions" class="headerlink" title="Common Text Funtions"></a>Common Text Funtions</h2><h3 id="Notes"><a href="#Notes" class="headerlink" title="Notes"></a>Notes</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note default %&#125; Default Content &#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% note primary %&#125; Primary Content &#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% note success %&#125; Success Content &#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% note info %&#125; Info Content &#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% note warning %&#125; Warning Content &#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% note danger %&#125; Danger Content &#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

