<h3 id="Labels"><a href="#Labels" class="headerlink" title="Labels"></a>Labels</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Label_1 </span><br><span class="line">&#123;% label primary@Label_2 %&#125; &#123;% label success@Label_3 %&#125; &#123;% label info@Label_4 %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">*&#123;% label warning @Label_5 %&#125;*  **&#123;% label danger@Label_6 %&#125;**  ~~&#123;% label default @Label_7 %&#125;~~</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% label @Label_8 %&#125;    &lt;mark&gt;Label_9&lt;/mark&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
